		<div id="recipes" class="left" data-role="content">
			<h3>Ingredients</h3>
		    <ul data-role="listview" data-inset="true">
		        <li>3 slices bread</li>
				<li>2 tablespoons fruit preserves, any flavor</li>
				<li>2 tablespoons peanut butter</li>
		    </ul>
		
		    <h3>Directions</h3>
		    <ol data-role="listview" data-inset="true">
		        <li>Toast 1 bread slice, allow to cool. Spread one side of each of the two remaining slices with preserves. Spread both sides of the toasted slice with peanut butter. Form a sandwich with the toasted slice in the center.</li>
			</ol>
		    <a href="http://allrecipes.com/recipe/ignacios-super-peanut-butter-and-jelly-sandwich/detail.aspx?event8=1&prop24=SR_Title&e11=peanut%20butter%20and%20jelly%20sandwich&e8=Quick%20Search&event10=1&e7=Recipe%20Search%20Results">Recipe from Allrecipes.com</a>
